# Walkthrough - SuperThanks Feature

## Prerequisites
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Firebase Configuration Required**
> You must run the following command in your terminal to generate the necessary `firebase_options.dart` file and configure your app for Android/iOS:
> ```bash
> flutterfire configure
> ```
> Follow the prompts to select your Firebase project. Without this, the app will crash or fail to send messages.

